Description: Creating a Load HMI button and status. 

Rev 1.0 - Initial Release 2/21/2025


Code Reference:
----------------------------
-- Digital Input Debounce Function --
-- User edits commented areas of code to set State/permissive letter.
-- In Example HMI Start-Up dashboard
	* In State 7, Permissive B shows how to set startup sequence for the Load button.
	* User can set this permissive for any state (NOT STATE 0), and either permissive A or B.
-- In Example
	* Push Start button
	* Once The Load Status turns yellow and shows "Ready To Load", user presses LOAD CONTROL toggle button to load unit.
----------------------------